<h2><a name='sect0' href='#toc0'>Name</a></h2>
<b>MPI_Type_get_extent</b>, <b><a href="../man3/MPI_Type_get_extent_x.3.php">MPI_Type_get_extent_x</a></b> - Returns the lower
bound and extent of a data type.
<p>
